{
  "texts": [
    "Then, we have",
    "Case 1 ≤ u ≤ κγ.",
    "In this case |V ∪ | = 2κγ + 2 -u and there are κγ -u vertices that appear only in π (2) (V) \\ π (1) (V).",
    "All these vertices belong to G ∆ and each such vertex is connected (within G ∆) to at least one vertex in the intersection π",
    "∆ ⊂ E ∆ be the set of edges of G ∆ that arise from π (2) [G]."
  ]
}